## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may not capture the full complexity of individual cases of domestic violence. Additionally, the data is primarily from Western contexts, which may not fully represent cultural variations in domestic violence causes and manifestations. Further research, including primary studies and cross-cultural analyses, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.